    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Doctrine that the universe is under the dominion of two opposing principles, one of which is good and the other evil.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
